init_oa_design_view(25.10)                          init_oa_design_view(25.10)

Name
       init_oa_design_view

Syntax
         init_oa_design_view <viewname>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies the OpenAccess design view name to be used. This global vari-
       able  replaces  the  previous rda_Input(ui_oa_designView) configuration
       file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies  myOAView  as  the  OpenAccess
                database view.

                set init_oa_design_view {myOAView}

Related Information
              * init_design

